# Overview
This mod provides a new framework for creating boss like creatures with skills, creating rendered arms and animated items, and using bedrock models and animations (geo.json and animation.json).
# Content
This mod provides:
- Particle effect template;
- Visual effect templates such as screen shake;
- Player animation template (not yet completed);
- Boss mob templates and skill templates, such as laser (skill templates are not yet completed);
- Animation system of mobs and items;
- JSON animation support for bedrock of mobs and items models;
- Item skill template;
- A relatively simple gun template (covering opening, reloading, inspection, and various visual effects);
